So I'll touch on that,

332
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,119
and things called LSP as well,

333
00:12:18,119 --> 00:12:19,119
which I didn't mention,

334
00:12:19,119 --> 00:12:20,440
which we'll get to too.

335
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:23,479
But the main topic for tomorrow is sandboxing,

336
